      "role": "user",
      "content": "small moments dont change anything. they just give me enough energy to start the cycle all over again. it's like a glitch. no matter what i do, i end up right back at the beginning, broken and exhausted. i feel like there's no actual way to break the loop. it's just... inevitable.",
